      • matchesFilter

        public boolean matchesFilter(ReportKey filter)
        Matching criteria -- pretty easy but should be put in English... - If the filter object has a null for a field, any value works. - If this report key has a null (for some reason) that works too - To compare, take the filter and do a starts with against the real key's value - For start date, this report key it must be LATER in time than the filter date
        Parameters:
        filter - a partially filled out report key that represents filter criteria
        Returns:
        true if this report key matches the filter defined by the given report key
